rComments: Pedro seemed very knowledgeable but you can easily pass without going to class except for tests. All homework is online through aplia and due every Sunday. He never takes attendance. He cracks some jokes and curses, so that livens it up a little, but he never uses the microphone so he can be hard to hear sometimes.

This class was terrible! Given it was his first semester teaching at West Virginia University I considered cutting him some slack, but he's no help at all! Don't even bother going to class because you'll have to teach yourself everything anyways. I DO NOT RECOMMEND
